---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// A now page (nownownow.com convention): what I'm focused on at this point in
// life. Hand-written — distinct from the auto-fed Now *section* on the homepage.
// Bump `lastUpdated` whenever you rewrite the copy.
const lastUpdated = '23 July 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Now — Pedro Castro"
  description="What I'm focused on at this point in my life."
>
  <article class="prose">
    <header>
      <h1>Now</h1>
      <p class="muted lede">
        I'm living in Lisbon, at a crossroads between the comfortable life I've
        been blessed with and the life I inevitably wish I had.
      </p>
    </header>

    <p>
      My focus at the moment is exploring technology and AI, building side
      projects, and redesigning my Higher Education engagements to capture this
      newly unlocked potential. I've gone from playing Counter-Strike and
      Cities: Skylines to building with
      <a href="https://claude.com/claude-code">Claude Code</a> in my spare time,
      trying to get better and better at capturing signals and translating them
      into products, features, or ideas worth chasing. Lately I've been thinking
      about how a generalist like me can find more purpose in the day to day.
    </p>

    <p>
      Offline, I've been sticking to running and indoor cycling, and I'm
      preparing for a couple of 8K/10K runs in September and October.
    </p>

    <p>
      Relationships-wise — and to my grandma's despair — there really is nothing
      to note. The apps don't suit me, so I'm honestly living my best single
      life, regardless of any
      <a href="https://www.gutenberg.org/files/1342/1342-h/1342-h.htm">truth
      universally acknowledged</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="now-note">
      This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about">now page</a>, inspired by
      <a href="https://nownownow.com">nownownow.com</a> — last updated {lastUpdated}.
      You can also see what I'm currently vibing to on
      <a href="/">the homepage</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  header { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lede { max-width: 34rem; }
  .now-note {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
</style>
